{"type":"message","id":"5495be0f","parentId":"93a15aef","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:50:51.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，数据抓取成功了，虽然抓取第4页失败了（可能被网站限流），但已保存了6027条记录。现在让我查看最新开奖结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yyvvze0yvf2s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/double-color-ball && python -c \"\nimport sqlite3\nconn = sqlite3.connect('data/double_color_ball.db')\ncursor = conn.cursor()\ncursor.execute('SELECT issue_number, draw_date, red_ball_1, red_ball_2, red_ball_3, red_ball_4, red_ball_5, red_ball_6, blue_ball FROM lottery_records ORDER BY draw_date DESC LIMIT 5')\nrows = cursor.fetchall()\nprint('🎲 最新双色球开奖结果：\\n')\nprint('='*50)\nfor row in rows:\n    issue = row[0]\n    date = row[1]\n    red = [row[2], row[3], row[4], row[5], row[6], row[7]]\n    blue = row[8]\n    red_str = ' '.join(f'{n:02d}' for n in sorted(red))\n    print(f'📅 {date} | 期号: {issue}')\n    print(f'   🔴 红球: {red_str} | 🔵 蓝球: {blue:02d}')\n    print('-'*50)\nconn.close()\n\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":426,"output":348,"cacheRead":51067,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778320244601,"responseId":"064e36748395d45b52f755c3fe99a09c"}}
